channel.title: Homes Under the Hammer
channel.desc: A tiger in a north London maisonette has Owain earning his stripes. Don't panic, it's not a real one! Meanwhile, Dion is dealing with damp in Kidsgrove, and Martel is in Hartlepool, where a two-bedroom mid-terrace has an intriguingly low guide price.
